<title>ITALY: Bank of Italy sets 3.0 billion mark repo tender.</title>
<headline>Bank of Italy sets 3.0 billion mark repo tender.</headline>
<dateline>ROME 1997-06-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Bank of Italy set a 3.0 billion mark repurchase tender for June 20 for resale on July 21.</p>
<p>The auction will be held tomorrow and the results will be announced soon afterwards.</p>
<p>The Bank said the lira/mark rate on which the tender will be based will be announced tomorrow morning.</p>
